I"t<p>After three Durga Puja photograph series : <a href="http://upamanyu.in/works/2013/sharodiya-13/">2013</a>, <a href="http://upamanyu.in/works/2015/sharodiya-15/">2015</a>  &amp; <a href="http://upamanyu.in/works/2016/sharodiya-16">2016</a> this is the fourth. A series photographing Durga idols of Kolkata and suburbs. Durga Puja, also called Durgotsava and Navaratri, is an annual Hindu festival in the Indian subcontinent that reveres the goddess Durga.</p>

